      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOVERING (6) was a last start winner (29.80) from Box 2 at this track. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Can continue on with his winning form. TARAWI SUSHI (2) was quickly into stride and burnt early from out wide where she gave a sight, finishing second (29.88) and beaten one length over 520m at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Expected to be in the finish again. ASCEND FERN (4) finished eighth last time at Grafton but could not have been more impressive a few runs back in his excellent 21.99 win at Gosford over 388m. Expected to feature on best figures. FEAR TO EXCEL (3) racing over this distance brings the best out in her.",
